<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 03:41:04 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>中国比亚迪新版畅销电动车价格低于前代</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-prices-new-version-best-selling-ev-lower-than-predecessor-2024-03-04/</link><description>随着全球最大汽车市场的价格战愈演愈烈，中国领先的电动汽车 (EV) 制造商比亚迪周一推出了其最畅销汽车的新版本，价格低于其停产前身的最终价格。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 03:12:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-prices-new-version-best-selling-ev-lower-than-predecessor-2024-03-04/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾进行海上巡逻以检查中国科考船的存在</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-conducts-marine-patrols-check-presence-chinese-research-ships-2024-03-04/</link><description>菲律宾周一部署一艘海岸警卫队船只在该国北部和东部海域执行为期两周的巡逻任务，以加强其海上存在，并对在宾汉隆起发现的中国科考船进行检查。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 02:05:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-conducts-marine-patrols-check-presence-chinese-research-ships-2024-03-04/</guid></item><item><title>韩国和美国军队开始针对朝鲜威胁的年度演习</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/south-korea-us-troops-kick-off-annual-drills-over-north-threats-2024-03-04/</link><description>官员们表示，韩国和美国军队周一开始了春季演习，参加的部队人数是去年的两倍，因为这两个盟国寻求更好地应对朝鲜日益增加的核威胁和导弹威胁。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 02:01:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/south-korea-us-troops-kick-off-annual-drills-over-north-threats-2024-03-04/</guid></item><item><title>等待美联储线索，美元走软；比特币创两年新高</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-eases-fed-clues-awaited-bitcoin-hits-2-year-high-2024-03-04/</link><description>受美国国债收益率下降的压力，美元周一走软，交易员等待更重要的经济数据，以获取有关美联储降息时机的新线索。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 01:49:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-eases-fed-clues-awaited-bitcoin-hits-2-year-high-2024-03-04/</guid></item><item><title>日经指数引领亚洲走高，未来一周活动精彩纷呈</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-03-04/</link><description>亚洲股市周一走强，日经指数再创新高，投资者准备迎接充满央行事件和重大数据的一周，这些数据将完善市场对利率何时开始下降的押注。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 00:22:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-03-04/</guid></item><item><title>澳大利亚欢迎东南亚领导人提供新的海事安全资金</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/australia-welcomes-southeast-asia-leaders-with-fresh-maritime-security-funding-2024-03-03/</link><description>澳大利亚周一表示，印度太平洋和东南亚国家正面临严重的国防威胁，因为它在与东南亚集团的峰会上为与东盟国家的海上安全协定拨出了更多资金。</description><pubDate>Sun, 03 Mar 2024 23:48:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/australia-welcomes-southeast-asia-leaders-with-fresh-maritime-security-funding-2024-03-03/</guid></item><item><title>美国资助法案阻止中国从战略石油储备购买石油</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/us-funding-bill-blocks-china-buying-oil-strategic-petroleum-reserve-2024-03-03/</link><description>国会领导人周日公布的美国资助立法中的一项措施将阻止中国从战略石油储备购买石油。</description><pubDate>Sun, 03 Mar 2024 23:34:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/us-funding-bill-blocks-china-buying-oil-strategic-petroleum-reserve-2024-03-03/</guid></item><item><title>早盘：全球情绪高涨，中国2024年计划迫在眉睫</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-03-03/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Sun, 03 Mar 2024 21:48:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-03-03/</guid></item><item><title>泰国协助将900名诈骗受害者从缅甸转移到中国</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/thailand-facilitates-transfer-900-scam-victims-myanmar-china-2024-03-03/</link><description>泰国总理斯雷塔·塔维辛 (Srettha Thavisin) 周日表示，泰国上周帮助将被困在缅甸边境城镇诈骗中心的约 900 名中国公民转移回中国。</description><pubDate>Sun, 03 Mar 2024 12:23:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/thailand-facilitates-transfer-900-scam-victims-myanmar-china-2024-03-03/</guid></item><item><title>马来西亚称 MH370 失踪 10 年后必须继续搜寻</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/malaysia-says-mh370-search-must-go-10-years-after-plane-vanished-2024-03-03/</link><description>马来西亚交通部长周日表示，随着该航班在世界上最大的航空谜团之一失踪十周年的临近，马来西亚正在推动重新搜寻马来西亚航空 MH370 航班。</description><pubDate>Sun, 03 Mar 2024 12:19:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/malaysia-says-mh370-search-must-go-10-years-after-plane-vanished-2024-03-03/</guid></item><item><title>韩国医生举行大规模集会反对医疗政策</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/south-korean-doctors-holds-mass-rally-against-medical-policy-2024-03-03/</link><description>数千名韩国医生周日举行大规模集会，反对政府增加医学院招生的计划，无视官方要求见习医生辞职以抗议重返工作岗位的呼吁。</description><pubDate>Sun, 03 Mar 2024 09:58:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/south-korean-doctors-holds-mass-rally-against-medical-policy-2024-03-03/</guid></item><item><title>韩国民众在心爱的大熊猫福宝返回中国前与她告别</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/south-koreans-bid-farewell-beloved-panda-fu-bao-before-her-return-china-2024-03-03/</link><description>周日，韩国一家动物园为在该国出生的第一只大熊猫“福宝”举办了欢送会，随后这只受人喜爱的动物将返回中国。</description><pubDate>Sun, 03 Mar 2024 07:26:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/south-koreans-bid-farewell-beloved-panda-fu-bao-before-her-return-china-2024-03-03/</guid></item><item><title>中国驻菲律宾使馆强烈谴责菲律宾特使涉南海言论</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-embassy-condemns-philippine-envoys-remarks-south-china-sea-2024-03-03/</link><description>中国驻菲律宾大使馆周日表示，“强烈”谴责菲律宾驻华盛顿大使最近的涉华言论，称其“无视基本事实”。</description><pubDate>Sun, 03 Mar 2024 06:27:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-embassy-condemns-philippine-envoys-remarks-south-china-sea-2024-03-03/</guid></item><item><title>莫斯科称俄罗斯和中国同意俄罗斯必须参加乌克兰谈判</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/moscow-says-russia-china-agree-that-russia-must-be-present-ukraine-talks-2024-03-02/</link><description>俄罗斯外交部周日表示，俄罗斯副外长米哈伊尔·加卢津和中国欧亚事务特别代表李辉表示，没有莫斯科的参与，不可能讨论乌克兰问题的解决方案。</description><pubDate>Sat, 02 Mar 2024 22:49:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/moscow-says-russia-china-agree-that-russia-must-be-present-ukraine-talks-2024-03-02/</guid></item><item><title>耶伦预计美国从智利的进口大幅增长，并关注绿色转型的进展</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/yellen-visits-us-lithium-site-chile-eyes-progress-green-transition-2024-03-02/</link><description>美国财政部长珍妮特·耶伦周六预测，对锂（电动汽车电池所需的核心部件）的需求不断扩大，将在未来几年大幅增加美国从智利的进口。</description><pubDate>Sat, 02 Mar 2024 19:10:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/yellen-visits-us-lithium-site-chile-eyes-progress-green-transition-2024-03-02/</guid></item></channel></rss>